        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="文章模板"><a href="#文章模板" class="headerlink" title="文章模板"></a>文章模板</h2><figure class="highlight subunit"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: My awesome title</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">date: 2019<span class="string">-07</span><span class="string">-14</span> 18:38:45</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">categories:</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">4</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    - Category1</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">5</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    - Category2</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">6</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">tags:</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">7</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    - Tag1</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">8</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">    - Tag2</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">9</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mp3: http://domain.com/awesome.mp3</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">10</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cover: http://domain.com/awesome.jpg</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">11</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">preview: 300</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>文章只有添加相关categories和tags会被自动识别，并生成相关链接</p><h2 id="分类页"><a href="#分类页" class="headerlink" title="分类页"></a>分类页</h2><p>创建分类页</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new<span class="built_in"> page </span>categories</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>分类页模板</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">categories</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2019</span><span class="number">-07</span><span class="number">-14</span> <span class="number">12</span><span class="string">:39:04</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">"categories"</span></span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="标签页"><a href="#标签页" class="headerlink" title="标签页"></a>标签页</h2><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new<span class="built_in"> page </span>tags</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>标签页模板</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">tags</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">2</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2014</span><span class="number">-12</span><span class="number">-22</span> <span class="number">12</span><span class="string">:39:04</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">3</span></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">"tags"</span></span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="参考文档"><a href="#参考文档" class="headerlink" title="参考文档"></a>参考文档</h2><ul><li><a href="https://github.com/TriDiamond/hexo-theme-obsidian" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方文档</a></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
